# 📦 Payment Repository — Complete Analysis

## Overview

This is a **Node.js / Express + MongoDB (Mongoose)** backend for an **Inventory & Sales Management System** tailored for a **pharmacy / medical supplies** business. It manages the full lifecycle of products, customers, invoicing, returns, payments, stock, purchase orders, prescriptions, expenses, and reporting — with PDF/Excel export capabilities.

### Authentication

- **POST `/auth/register`** — public signup (name, email, password). New users get role `USER` and receive a **JWT** in the response (same shape as login).
- **POST `/auth/login`** — email + password → JWT.
- **GET `/auth/me`** — current user (requires `Authorization: Bearer`).

There is no “first admin only” or tenant-gated registration; duplicate emails return **409**.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Runtime | Node.js 20 (Alpine Docker) |
| Framework | Express 4 |
| Database | MongoDB (via Mongoose 8) |
| Validation | Joi |
| Export | ExcelJS, XLSX, PDFKit |
| Dev Tools | Nodemon, Prettier, Concurrently |

---

## Project Structure

```
payment/
├── index.js                 # Entry point — DB connect + server start
├── app.js                   # Express app — middleware + route mounting
├── Dockerfile               # Node 20 Alpine container
├── package.json             # Dependencies & scripts
├── .env/.env                # Environment variables (DB URI, password)
│
├── models/                  # 16 Mongoose schemas
│   ├── invoice.js           # Invoice with line items, statuses, pre-save hooks
│   ├── product.js           # Product catalog (pricing, barcode, images)
│   ├── customer.js          # Customer with balance tracking & linked docs
│   ├── payment.js           # Customer payments (Cash/Card/Transfer)
│   ├── return.js            # Product returns with soft delete
│   ├── stock.js             # Per-product stock tracking
│   ├── transactions.js      # Debit/credit transaction ledger
│   ├── sales.js             # Sales order aggregation
│   ├── category.js          # Hierarchical categories (virtuals)
│   ├── supplier.js          # Supplier directory
│   ├── supplierPayment.model.js  # Payments to suppliers
│   ├── purchaseOrder.model.js    # Purchase orders with receiving
│   ├── prescription.model.js     # Medical prescriptions (doctor, dosage)
│   ├── expense.model.js     # Business expenses (recurring, categorized)
│   ├── cashTransaction.model.js  # Cash flow tracking (income/expense)
│   └── counter.js           # Auto-increment counter for sequences
│
├── controllers/             # 16 controllers + helpers
