> [!NOTE]
> - **No Authentication/Authorization**: No auth middleware (JWT handlers exist in error handler but no auth routes/middleware).
> - **No Tests**: [package.json](file:///c:/Users/Mohamed%20Elafandy/Desktop/cmder/payment/package.json) has `"test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\""`. No test framework installed.
> - **`body-parser` is redundant**: `express.json()` is already used; `body-parser` is imported but not called.
> - **[.env](file:///c:/Users/Mohamed%20Elafandy/Desktop/cmder/payment/.env/.env) path**: Config loads from [./.env/.env](file:///c:/Users/Mohamed%20Elafandy/Desktop/cmder/payment/.env/.env) (nested directory), which is unusual.
> - **Pagination bug in `crudFactory.getAll`**: [paginate](file:///c:/Users/Mohamed%20Elafandy/Desktop/cmder/payment/utils/features.js#43-52) response uses `doc.length` (already paginated result count) instead of total document count.
> - **Production error handling bug**: [globalError.js](file:///c:/Users/Mohamed%20Elafandy/Desktop/cmder/payment/controllers/globalError.js) lines 81-85 call error handlers but don't reassign the error variable, so the transformed error is never used.
> - **Inconsistent file naming**: Some models use [.model.js](file:///c:/Users/Mohamed%20Elafandy/Desktop/cmder/payment/models/expense.model.js) suffix, others don't.
